I think, I don't...

01:20:34.899 --> 01:20:35.761
- I'm sorry.

01:20:37.867 --> 01:20:38.661
- It's okay.

01:20:50.776 --> 01:20:52.882
[gasping]

01:20:54.884 --> 01:20:56.092
